{"id": "1e83488d-16fa-4583-bf2b-a3e1b98b0c22", "task_id": "277f2c2d-1493-4277-885d-52c8ad763043", "path": "backend/templates/index.html", "artifact_type": "file", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>{{ title }}</title>\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --dark-bg: #0a0a0f;\n            --accent-blue: #00e5ff; /* Cyan-blue */\n            --accent-purple: #ff00ff; /* Magenta */\n            --accent-green: #00ff88; /* Bright Green */\n            --text-color: #e0e0e0;\n            --form-bg: rgba(15, 15, 20, 0.8);\n            --input-bg: #1c1c24;\n            --input-border: #444;\n            --glow-strength: 0 0 10px; /* Base glow effect */\n        }\n\n        * {\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;\n            background-color: var(--dark-bg);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            overflow: hidden; /* Hide potential scrollbars from animations */\n            position: relative;\n            text-shadow: var(--glow-strength) var(--accent-blue);\n        }\n\n        /* Glitch effect background */\n        .glitch-effect {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(0,229,255,0.05) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 70%),\n                        repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0,229,255,0.02) 0, rgba(0,255,136,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 3px);\n            animation: glitch-bg 15s infinite alternate linear;\n            pointer-events: none;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes glitch-bg {\n            0% { background-position: 0 0; }\n            100% { background-position: 100% 100%; }\n        }\n\n        .login-container {\n            background: var(--form-bg);\n            border: 2px solid var(--accent-blue);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 40px;\n            box-shadow: var(--glow-strength) var(--accent-blue);\n            text-align: center;\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 400px;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1; /* Ensure it's above the glitch effect */\n            animation: neon-border-pulse 5s infinite ease-in-out alternate;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes neon-border-pulse {\n            0% {\n                border-color: var(--accent-blue);\n                box-shadow: var(--glow-strength) var(--accent-blue);\n            }\n            33% {\n                border-color: var(--accent-purple);\n                box-shadow: var(--glow-strength) var(--accent-purple);\n            }\n            66% {\n                border-color: var(--accent-green);\n                box-shadow: var(--glow-strength) var(--accent-green);\n            }\n            100% {\n                border-color: var(--accent-blue);\n                box-shadow: var(--glow-strength) var(--accent-blue);\n            }\n        }\n\n        .login-title {\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            color: var(--accent-green);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--accent-green), 0 0 30px var(--accent-green);\n            letter-spacing: 3px;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n\n        .login-form .form-group {\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .login-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .login-form input[type=\"password\"] {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 15px 20px;\n            background-color: var(--input-bg);\n            border: 1px solid var(--input-border);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            color: var(--accent-blue);\n            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            outline: none;\n            transition: border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-shadow: none; /* Remove global text-shadow */\n        }\n\n        .login-form input::placeholder {\n            color: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .login-form input:focus {\n            border-color: var(--accent-blue);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.6);\n        }\n\n        /* Hidden label for accessibility */\n        .sr-only {\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 1px;\n            height: 1px;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: -1px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);\n            white-space: nowrap;\n            border: 0;\n        }\n\n        .login-button {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 15px 20px;\n            background-color: var(--accent-purple);\n            border: 2px solid var(--accent-purple);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;\n            text-shadow: none; /* Remove global text-shadow */\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        .login-button:hover {\n            background-color: #ff33ff; /* Lighter purple */\n            border-color: #ff33ff;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.8), 0 0 25px rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .signup-link {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-shadow: none;\n        }\n\n        .signup-link a {\n            color: var(--accent-green);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease, text-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-shadow: none;\n        }\n\n        .signup-link a:hover {\n            color: #00ffaa; /* Lighter green */\n            text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        /* Scanline effect */\n        .scanline {\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(\n                to bottom,\n                transparent 0%,\n                rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.3) 50%,\n                transparent 100%\n            );\n            pointer-events: none;\n            animation: scanline 8s linear infinite;\n            opacity: 0.2;\n            z-index: 9999;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes scanline {\n            0% {\n                transform: translateY(-100%);\n            }\n            100% {\n                transform: translateY(100%);\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"glitch-effect\"></div>\n    <div class=\"login-container\">\n        <h1 class=\"login-title\">N E O - K Y O T O <br> L O G I N</h1>\n        <form action=\"/login\" method=\"post\" class=\"login-form\">\n            <div class=\"form-group\">\n                <label for=\"username\" class=\"sr-only\">Username</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"username\" name=\"username\" placeholder=\"JACK IN_ (Username)\" required>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"form-group\">\n                <label for=\"password\" class=\"sr-only\">Password</label>\n                <input type=\"password\" id=\"password\" name=\"password\" placeholder=\"ACCESS_CODE (Password)\" required>\n            </div>\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"login-button\">INITIATE_PROTOCOL</button>\n            <p class=\"signup-link\">NO_ACCESS? <a href=\"#\">REGISTER_NEW_UNIT</a></p>\n        </form>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"scanline\"></div>\n</body>\n</html>\n", "metadata": {"language": "html", "framework": "static_html", "explanation": "This HTML document creates a cyberpunk-themed login page. It uses Jinja2 templating for the page title (`{{ title }}`). The layout is centered with a form that posts to the `/login` endpoint. CSS is embedded to provide a dark, neon-lit aesthetic, featuring 'Orbitron' and 'Share Tech Mono' fonts, glowing elements, and subtle background animations like a 'glitch effect' and 'scanlines' to enhance the futuristic, retro-tech feel. Form inputs and buttons are styled to match the theme with interactive hover/focus states. Accessibility is considered with `sr-only` labels for inputs.", "dependencies": ["https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap"]}, "created_at": "2026-05-16 16:43:22.345643"}